HEADWORD: directivity
<hw>directivity</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the property of a microphone or
antenna of being more sensitive to sounds coming from one direction than
from another.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> directionality.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

